    {
      "text": "Pet Club: Neko Daisuki! (ペット倶楽部 ねこ大すき！, Pet Cat Club Hiroshi Suki!) is a video game released in Japan for the Game Gear. It is similar to Pet Club: Inu Daisuki! except it deals with taking care of a newborn kitten (from its birth until it reaches maturity) instead of a puppy. The game is part of Kid's Gear collection of titles for a younger audience.\nThere is a cameo to Sonic the Hedgehog in one of the playable rooms in the game.",
